snippet.title: Scoot Scoot Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1570310/Scoot_Scoot/

Explore and race in iconic locations. Ride enigmatic bikes and express yourself with deep customization. Take on complex gymkhana courses, open world checkpoint races and hectic delivery missions.

Music - Pelagic Journey By Purrple Cat - licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0
